title: Hawaiian Bread Rolls
ingredients: ['350ml warm water (45 degrees C)', '1 egg', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '1 teaspoon lemon extract', '1 tablespoon black treacle', '1 tablespoon honey', '5 tablespoons caster sugar', '2 tablespoons dried milk powder', '25g butter flavoured margarine', '615g bread flour', '2 teaspoons dried active baking yeast']
